title: 48: Halloween Stores in Virginia Beach, VA
description:
WHEN YOU YELL, I YELP! 
Looking for a nose to pick? You've come to the right place. Turn up the Ziggy Idol, put on your star costume, and join us as we kick off spooky-ooky season with Halloween stores in Virginia Beach, VA! 

Support us on Patreon at patreon.com/beachtoosandy to fulfill our dream of chatting with you live on video. 
Buy our merch! https://store.dftba.com/collections/beach-too-sandy-water-too-wet

Logo by Courtney DeKorte. Theme by Mavus White.
Music by PSOVOD, tyops, and RichardCulver.
